      "title": "Japan will not help SL now",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Japanese Ambassador in Colombo Mizukoshi Hideaki who met the TNA yesterday had reportedly said that there is a risk of financial assistance to Sri Lanka being mismanaged and hence Japan will not support the country at this point."
